sd=Underwriting	This service domain manages the underwriting decision process for products as appropriate (including many loan types and some insurance products)	A corporate loan offer is processed and at the appropriate point an underwriting authorization is requested	The underwriting decision considers the ability of the borrower to finance the loan based on their known cash flows and credit worthiness. The underwriting decision refers to specific properties of the proposed loan (amount, term, repayment schedule, collateral etc.), the income and known commitments of the borrower and their credit history with the bank. The decision may factor perceived underwriting risks into the interest rate and/or collateral requirements to obtain approval
sdpath=underwriting
crpath=underwriting-assessment
crr=Underwriting Assessment Instance
mcr=Underwriting Assessment
bqs=
CONFIG
UnderwritingAssessment	evaluate	Evaluate an underwriting decision		evaluateUnderwritingAssessment		#desc
UnderwritingAssessment	update	Update details for an underwriting assessment		updateUnderwritingAssessment		#desc
UnderwritingAssessment	exchange	Accept, reject verify etc. an underwriting assessment		exchangeUnderwritingAssessment		#desc
UnderwritingAssessment	execute	Execute an automated task for an assessment (e.g. submit transactions)		executeUnderwritingAssessment		#desc
UnderwritingAssessment	request	Request manual intervention in an assessment (e.g. discussion)		requestUnderwritingAssessment		#desc
UnderwritingAssessment	grant	Obtain grant of authority from underwriting		grantUnderwritingAssessment		#desc
UnderwritingAssessment	retrieve	Retrieve details about an underwriting assessment		retrieveUnderwritingAssessment		#desc
